Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_lef_check_mask_shifts(25.10)            init_lef_check_mask_shifts(25.10)

Name
       init_lef_check_mask_shifts

Syntax
       init_lef_check_mask_shifts {on | off | bypass}

       Type: Enum

       Default: off

       Checks conflicts between the LEF FIXEDMASK and LAYERMASKSHIFT values in
       the  technology  and  MACRO sections when reading in any LEF files. You
       can set the following values:

              * on: When the variable is set as on, the the  tool  will  check
                for the conflict. In case of a conflict, the tool will give an
                error and stop running.

              * off: When the variable is set to off, the tool will  not check
                for the conflict.

              * bypass: When the variable is set as bypass, the tool will give
                and error message and will continue running.

Related Information
              * restoreDesign

